@node Main "Brikabrak - Documentation"

                             'Brikabrak' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Brikabrak' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you have to move tiles so
3 or more tiles of the same type are placed next to each other. To
complicate matters a little bit, tiles can only move in the
direction indicated by arrows that are shown at the right of the
game board.

  Try to place as many tiles of the same type together as you can,
but avoid leaving only 1 or 2 tiles of any type on the board...

  Have fun!

